  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Slice the whole wheat bread into 1-inch thick slices.",
    "Place the bread slices on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Drizzle the olive oil over the bread slices.",
    "Sprinkle the garlic powder, salt, and pepper over the bread slices.",
    "Bake the bread slices in the preheated oven for 5 minutes.",
    "Remove the bread slices from the oven and let them cool for 2 minutes.",
    "Top each bread slice with a quarter cup of pitted black olives.",
    "Sprinkle the chopped fresh parsley over the black olives.",
    "Drizzle the lemon juice over the parsley."
  ],
